<section class="bio-section">
  <div class="section-label">// Biography</div>
  <div class="bio-grid">
    <div class="bio-text">
      <p class="lede">Some pedal steel players fill a role. Kevin "The General" Neal defines the sound of a record.</p>
      <p>A university-trained musician with an instinct for the spaces between notes, The General has built one of the most respected reputations in Canadian country music &mdash; not through self-promotion, but through the undeniable authority of his playing. His stage name wasn't chosen. It was earned.</p>
      <p>Kevin has shared stages with some of the biggest names in North American country, performing at landmark venues and festivals including the <strong>Calgary Stampede</strong>, <strong>Mariposa Folk Festival</strong>, and other major festival stages around the world.</p>
      <p>In the studio, Kevin is equally at home. He has recorded with artists across multiple genres and continents, and is a trusted first call for session work at every level. Whether it's a major-label cut or an independent record, he brings the same attention and authority to every track.</p>
      <p>Twice nominated for <strong>CCMA Pedal Steel Player of the Year</strong>, Kevin's credentials come from the people who know the instrument best &mdash; fellow musicians and industry peers who recognize the rare combination of technical mastery and musical intelligence he brings to every room.</p>
      <p>His approach is systematic, tactical, and unfailingly musical. He reads a room, serves the song, and elevates the artist. That's why they call him The General.</p>

      <div class="bio-image">
        <img src="/kevin2.png" alt="Kevin Neal performing live on pedal steel" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="credentials">
      <div class="credential-item">
        <div class="credential-year">Live</div>
        <div class="credential-title">Grand Ole Opry</div>
        <div class="credential-sub">Nashville, Tennessee</div>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-item">
        <div class="credential-year">Festivals</div>
        <div class="credential-title">Calgary Stampede · Mariposa</div>
        <div class="credential-sub">+ Major stages in Norway & beyond</div>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-item">
        <div class="credential-year">Shared Stage</div>
        <div class="credential-title">Darius Rucker · Midland</div>
        <div class="credential-sub">+ Countless artists large and small</div>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-item">
        <div class="credential-year">Studio</div>
        <div class="credential-title">Session Work — Canada, US & Worldwide</div>
        <div class="credential-sub">Incl. Jade Eagleson touring & recording</div>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-item">
        <div class="credential-year">Multiple</div>
        <div class="credential-title">CCMA Pedal Steel Player of the Year</div>
        <div class="credential-sub">2&times; Nominated</div>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-item">
        <div class="credential-year">Education</div>
        <div class="credential-title">University Trained Musician</div>
        <div class="credential-sub">Multi-Instrument</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bio-section {
    padding: 100px 60px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .bio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .bio-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .bio-text p + p {
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .bio-text .lede {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--cream);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .bio-image {
    margin-top: 48px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.15);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bio-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .bio-text :global(strong) {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .credentials {
    position: sticky;
    top: 40px;
  }

  .credential-item {
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.15);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards;
  }

  .credential-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .credential-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }
  .credential-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .credential-item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.65s; }
  .credential-item:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .credential-item:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.95s; }

  .credential-year {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .credential-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .credential-sub {
    font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--light-mid);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .bio-section { padding: 60px 32px; }
    .bio-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .credentials { position: static; }
  }
</style>
